00:36.521 --> 00:39.306
Oh, dear!

00:40.760 --> 00:43.394
I'm sorry, did
I wake you up?

00:43.396 --> 00:44.812
What are you doing?

00:44.814 --> 00:49.200
I was trying to find
a nice way to wake you up.

00:49.202 --> 00:51.285
Well, kudos, you found one.

00:51.287 --> 00:54.572
Here. Merry day
before Christmas.

00:54.574 --> 00:56.907
I thought we agreed not
to exchange presents.

00:56.909 --> 01:00.461
Well, you gave me a pretty
nice present last night.

01:00.463 --> 01:01.829
Actually two.

01:01.831 --> 01:04.165
You're terrible.

01:04.167 --> 01:05.633
Open it.

01:10.005 --> 01:14.725
Dare I say it?
Key to your heart?

01:14.727 --> 01:16.644
Better. It's a key
to my house.

01:16.646 --> 01:20.731
Walden, I can't accept
a key to your house.

01:20.733 --> 01:22.900
It's a bit premature.

01:22.902 --> 01:25.186
Well, if anything in our
relationship's going to be premature,

01:25.188 --> 01:27.071
I prefer it to be
the house key.

01:27.073 --> 01:30.474
It's a very sweet gesture.

01:32.494 --> 01:33.861
Mistletoe.

01:35.580 --> 01:36.864
Oh, my!

01:36.866 --> 01:39.066
I've got to pick up my daughter
from her father's

01:39.068 --> 01:41.919
and I've got to get to the
airport to pick up my parents.

01:41.921 --> 01:43.754
Are you sure I can't
come with you?

01:43.756 --> 01:44.789
Positive.

01:44.791 --> 01:46.841
Why not?
We get along great.

01:46.843 --> 01:49.260
Your parents are in town,
my mom's coming to visit.

01:49.262 --> 01:50.544
It's Christmas.

01:50.546 --> 01:53.013
What better time for everybody
to get to know each other?

01:53.015 --> 01:55.516
Walden, we're still
getting to know each other.

01:55.518 --> 01:58.052
- I know you.
- Really?

01:58.054 --> 02:00.271
What color
are my eyes then?

02:00.273 --> 02:02.807
Brown. the left one's got a
little fleck of green in it.

02:02.809 --> 02:04.892
Damn.

02:04.894 --> 02:09.062
You say you're a size two,
but you're actually a size four.

02:09.065 --> 02:10.681
You run the water
in the bathroom

02:10.683 --> 02:14.201
to cover the sound
of you peeing.

02:14.203 --> 02:17.354
All right fine. Let me put it
another way.

02:17.356 --> 02:19.156
No families this year.

02:19.158 --> 02:22.293
And I am a size two.

02:23.128 --> 02:25.045
Merry Christmas.

02:25.864 --> 02:28.198
She took the key.

02:30.719 --> 02:33.203
Aw!

02:33.205 --> 02:35.890
♪ Men, men, men, men, manly men,
men, men ♪

02:35.892 --> 02:37.706
♪ Ah. ♪
♪ Men. ♪

02:37.707 --> 02:40.107
