15:57.133 --> 15:59.133
Hello?

15:59.135 --> 16:00.417
Oh, uh, hi, Zoey.

16:00.419 --> 16:03.220
Walden's not here.

16:03.222 --> 16:04.438
Really?

16:04.440 --> 16:07.141
Okay, well, well, thanks
