18:01.139 --> 18:02.756
Get out of here!

18:02.758 --> 18:04.091
It's all right!

18:04.093 --> 18:07.261
It's just a mother issue!

18:07.263 --> 18:11.232
Walden, you come down
from there right now!

18:11.234 --> 18:12.933
Oh, excuse me?

18:12.935 --> 18:14.602
Are you Walden's mum?

18:14.604 --> 18:16.654
Yes. Are-Are you Zoey?

18:16.656 --> 18:19.056
- I am.
